:24px;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Ja, beim Rasierhobel darfst du einmal in Qualität investieren. Dafür sparst du aber langfristig. Mit 20 Cent pro Klinge, die du 2-3 Mal nutzen kannst, kommst du deutlich günstiger Weg.</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="1a5b80b1-1b18-4cd3-97cb-cf221cebb9ba" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0" class="rmq-f42af9cd rmq-dd0ea640 rmq-1f47714 rmq-4a86ea09 alchemy-rte" style="display:none;font-size:20px;line-height:24px;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><h1><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">✅ Gut für dich, gut für die Umwelt</span></strong></h1></span></div><div data-rid="571e1311-4d20-4966-ac0d-5eb58212ce44" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0" class="rmq-4e3a3726 rmq-6100eebd rmq-1f47714 rmq-4a86ea09 alchemy-rte" style="display:none;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Wie du merkst ist die klassische Rasur gut für dich. Das wars aber noch nicht. Dadurch, dass du keinen Plastikmüll produzierst, schonst du auch die Umwelt. Die Klingen können ohne schlechtes Gewissen im Hausmüll entsorgt werden.</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="6dc7dda5-177b-4aaa-a0f4-a282938dee1e" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0" class="rmq-f42af9cd rmq-dd0ea640 rmq-1f47714 rmq-4a86ea09 alchemy-rte" style="display:none;font-size:20px;line-height:24px;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><h1><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">✅ </span><span style="color: #000000FF">Edles Design</span></strong></h1></span></div><div data-rid="c7f27ca0-4cab-4e89-a68c-cd22e777524f" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0" class="rmq-4e3a3726 rmq-dd0ea640 rmq-1f47714 rmq-4a86ea09 alchemy-rte" style="display:none;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Im Gegensatz zum Standard Rasierer macht das Design des Hobel auch einfach was her.</span></p></span></div><a data-rid="661a62cd-f1c6-413f-82c0-ee09533108af" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0" tabindex="0" role="button" class="rmq-434f9ccd rmq-346a129a rmq-e3e5ac0e rmq-efd51653 text alchemy-rte" style="text-align:center;display:none;align-self:stretch;padding-top:20px;padding-left:32px;padding-right:32px;padding-bottom:20px;background-color:#F3BC7F;border-top-left-radius:14px;border-top-right-radius:14px;border-bottom-left-radius:14px;border-bottom-right-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;cursor:pointer" data-radium="true"><div data-rid="d39e0f88-4368-4bcb-b132-0a8fa7caf75d" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0" class="rmq-4218833d rmq-74be85ff rmq-78bf3fea rmq-82b55d77 alchemy-rte" style="color:#FFFFFF;flex-grow:1;font-size:20px;font-weight:400;line-height:20px;letter-spacing:2px;flex-shrink:1;flex-basis:0;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><p><strong>Weniger Hautirritationen &amp; Rasierpickel</strong></p></span></div></a><div data-rid="9ee5ff9d-b350-490a-ac8b-0f4da3a8893e" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0" class="rmq-72b7c34d rmq-dd0ea640 rmq-1f47714 rmq-4a86ea09 alchemy-rte" style="display:none;font-size:20px;line-height:24px;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><h1><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Du bist noch nicht ganz überzeugt?</span></strong></h1></span></div><div data-rid="31a70d8a-