ink:0;flex-basis:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><p>Keine Hautirritationen &amp; Schnitte</p></span></div><div data-rid="13c6cb6d-82fc-451a-929e-a8f6da615c85" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0.0" class="rmq-38cb64a4 rmq-76e98407 rmq-1f47714 rmq-4a86ea09 alchemy-rte" style="font-size:16px;font-weight:400;line-height:27px;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Anfangs war ich etwas skeptisch, da ich so viele Rasierer probiert habe und immer Hautirritationen hatte. Jetzt mit Störtebekker bin ich voll kommen zufrieden, keine schnitte keine hautiritationen und immer eine perfekte Rasur. Vielen vielen Dank dafür</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="9845a17c-c212-43f8-ac64-269f0246a331" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0.0" class="rmq-f874de69 rmq-c778ca77 rmq-ca9f82e2 rmq-4eb93f7f alchemy-rte" style="font-size:16px;align-self:stretch;text-align:right;font-weight:700;line-height:27px;text-align-last:right;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word" data-radium="true"><span contenteditable="false" style="width:100%" data-radium="true"><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">- Theodor Benke</span></strong></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="5e9b30ab-0ab0-4141-8de8-bda3e3b902d5" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0" style="display:flex;max-width:100%;align-self:stretch;align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto;row-gap:10px;column-gap:10px;position:relative;min-width:var(--rmw, auto);min-height:var(--rmh, auto);--rmw:auto;--rmh:auto" class="rmq-44a7cdfe rmq-25062f1c rmq-5ec198a9 rmq-ced74b94" data-radium="true"><div data-rid="e188fd3c-8d77-4f72-818e-b001d5d61d4d" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0.0" style="display:flex;flex-shrink:0;flex-basis:auto" class="rmq-7d750a4